This verification for the diagnostics_ob package mirrors the standard MITgcm verification procedure.

This directory contains the following components:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
New Source Files
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The directory new_src_inc_files contains files which will eventually be update those in model/src and model/inc
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Tutorials
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The verification of the package uses the verification framework of the MITgcm, with the new package and other pertinent files.

To run the verification for for all configurations, run the following steps:
 - setup_all.sh
     - link files from verification, create masks for testing
 - build_all.sh
     - standard build steps for MITgcm models using MPI (edit with your system's opt file)
 - run_all.sh
     - standard run steps for MITgcm models using MPI

To return the verification back to its initial state, use reset.sh
-----------------------------------------------------------------------


-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Notebooks
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Here, we provide a series of notebooks that are used to compare/visualize the outputs from the new package in reference to those from the tutorials.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
